Hey guys, I just made this topic to release this basic black jack game I made.

Download: [url=https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/59761129/BlackJack/BlackJack.jar]https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/59761129/BlackJack/BlackJack.jar[/url]

For the record, I went through hell to make a card sprite sheet. Here is the drawing method for the cards (fun fun fun)

[code]public void drawCards(Graphics g) {

        for (int i = 0; i < Data.playerHand.getCardCount(); i++) {
            drawImage(g, new Rectangle(10 + ((i % 8) * 65) + ((i % 8) * 10), (int) (10 + Math.ceil(i / 8) * 100) + ((int) Math.ceil(i / 8) * 10), 65, 100), new Rectangle((Data.playerHand.getCard(i).getValue() * 65) - 65, (Data.playerHand.getCard(i).getSuit() * 100) - 100, 65, 100));
        }
    }

    public void drawImage(Graphics g, Rectangle destination, Rectangle source) {

        g.drawImage(Frame.sheet, destination.x, destination.y, destination.x + destination.width, destination.y + destination.height, source.x, source.y, source.x + source.width, source.y + source.height, this);
    }[/code]
